{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"\"The Better Man.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":8000,"text":"I was the better at getting and keeping."}]},{"cues":[{"time":12000,"text":"You were the better at spend and spend;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":16000,"text":"I was the better at grubbing and heaping,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"But who was the better man in the end?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":23000,"text":"Yes, who was the better man, my friend?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":27000,"text":"You were the better with lords and ladies,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"I was the better at pillaging Troy;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":33000,"text":"You were the better at kissing the babies,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"I was the better at search and destroy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41000,"text":"But who was the better man, old boy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":45000,"text":"Who was the better man?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"I was the better at improvisation,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51000,"text":"You were the better at spinning the plates;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"I was the better at procrastination,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":58000,"text":"You were the better at quiet debate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61000,"text":"But who was the better man, old mate?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"Who was the better man?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":68000,"text":"You were the better at rolling a reefer,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":72000,"text":"I was the better at coke and rum;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76000,"text":"Remember that night on the beach in Ibiza?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"The Maori twins"},{"time":82000,"text":"with the tattooed bum?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":85000,"text":"But who was the better man, old chum?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"Who was the better man?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"Now we come down to it, relatives grieving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95000,"text":"Out in the hall with their crocodile tears;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"Now that you're out of it, now that you're leaving,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"Now that they've sealed your arse and your ears,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"What I've been meaning to tell you for years,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"And years, and years, and years, old friend ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"Is that you were the better man, in the end;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":119000,"text":"You were the better man,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":122000,"text":"My friend."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":134000,"text":"I wrote this next poem for my mother."},{"time":137000,"text":"Every one of us had a mother,"},{"time":139000,"text":"only one --"},{"time":141000,"text":"probably the most important person in your life,"},{"time":143000,"text":"if you're lucky enough to know them."},{"time":147000,"text":"My mother was certainly the most important in mine."},{"time":151000,"text":"Let me try and describe her to you."},{"time":155000,"text":"She's 86 years old. She's frail."},{"time":159000,"text":"White, platinum hair."},{"time":163000,"text":"Why do they do that? Why do old ladies go to those hair shops,"},{"time":166000,"text":"and make those helmets?"},{"time":169000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":170000,"text":"Bright as a button. All the ducks in a row."},{"time":174000,"text":"Looks like a much prettier version"},{"time":178000,"text":"of Margaret Thatcher,"},{"time":180000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":182000,"text":"but without any of the soft bits in Margaret's character."},{"time":185000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":190000,"text":"I wrote this poem for her. These are not my beliefs."},{"time":193000,"text":"But my mother has lived by this creed"},{"time":196000,"text":"all her life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198000,"text":"\"Never Go Back.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":205000,"text":"Never go back. Never go back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"Never return to the haunts of your youth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"Keep to the track, to the beaten track;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":214000,"text":"Memory holds all you need of the truth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"Never look back. Never look back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221000,"text":"Never succumb to the gorgon's stare."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224000,"text":"Keep to the track, to the beaten track;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":229000,"text":"No-one is waiting and nothing is there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233000,"text":"Never go back. Never go back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"Never surrender the future you earned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":238000,"text":"Keep to the track, to the beaten track;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":242000,"text":"Never return to the bridges you've burned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"Never look back. Never look back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"Never retreat to the 'glorious past.'"}]},{"cues":[{"time":252000,"text":"Keep to the track, to the beaten track;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":255000,"text":"Treat every day of your life as your last."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258000,"text":"Never go back. Never go back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262000,"text":"Never acknowledge the ghost on the stair."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267000,"text":"Keep to the track, to the beaten track;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":271000,"text":"No-one is waiting and nothing is there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":285000,"text":"Now ladies and gentlemen, I'm up on me hobbyhorse."},{"time":287000,"text":"If every commercially minded cosmetic surgeon"},{"time":289000,"text":"were tied end to end along a railroad track,"},{"time":292000,"text":"that would be me,"},{"time":294000,"text":"stoking the train"},{"time":296000,"text":"without a qualm in the world."},{"time":298000,"text":"Ladies, don't do it."},{"time":302000,"text":"Don't do it."},{"time":305000,"text":"You think we want you to do it, but we don't want you to do it."},{"time":308000,"text":"Stop it."},{"time":310000,"text":"Tell them to go to hell."},{"time":313000,"text":"You bodies are wonderful as they are."},{"time":316000,"text":"Just leave them alone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"\"To a Beautiful Lady of a Certain Age.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":325000,"text":"Lady lady, do not weep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327000,"text":"What is gone is gone. Now sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"Turn your pillow. Dry your tears."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335000,"text":"Count thy sheep and not thy years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339000,"text":"Nothing good can come of this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":341000,"text":"Time rules all, my dearest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"'Tis but folly to be waging war"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"On one who never lost before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"Lady, this is all in vain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"Youth can never come again;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":357000,"text":"We have drunk the summer wine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"None can make a stitch in time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362000,"text":"Nip and tuck till crack of doom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364000,"text":"What is foretold in the womb"}]},{"cues":[{"time":367000,"text":"May not be foresworn with gold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372000,"text":"Nor may time be bought or sold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376000,"text":"Dearest, do I love thee less?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":383000,"text":"Do I shrink from thy caress?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":386000,"text":"Think you I could cease to care?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":389000,"text":"Never was there one so fair!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":393000,"text":"Lady lady, do not weep --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":395000,"text":"What is gone is gone. Now sleep."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400000,"text":"Lean against me, calm your fears,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":404000,"text":"Count thy blessings, not thy years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":419000,"text":"America, ladies and gentlemen, has done more for me financially than Britain"},{"time":422000,"text":"ever has, or ever could have done."},{"time":424000,"text":"I was born in Britain, as you have probably guessed."},{"time":428000,"text":"Even when on its worst behavior,"},{"time":430000,"text":"I find myself automatically defending the USA"},{"time":433000,"text":"from the sneers of green-eyed Europhiles"},{"time":436000,"text":"playing their Greek card to Roman trumps."},{"time":441000,"text":"America is an empire."},{"time":444000,"text":"I hope you know that now."},{"time":447000,"text":"All empires, by definition, are bumbling,"},{"time":450000,"text":"shambolic, bullying, bureaucratic affairs,"},{"time":455000,"text":"as certain of the rightness of their cause in infancy,"},{"time":458000,"text":"as they are corrupted by power in their dotage."},{"time":463000,"text":"I am no historian, ladies and gentlemen."},{"time":466000,"text":"But it seems to be that the USA's sins,"},{"time":469000,"text":"compared to those of many previous empires,"},{"time":474000,"text":"are of a more moderate,"},{"time":478000,"text":"if more pervasive, kind."},{"time":481000,"text":"Let me put this bluntly."},{"time":483000,"text":"If Americans are so fat,"},{"time":485000,"text":"stupid and ignorant,"},{"time":488000,"text":"my dear friends from Birmingham,"},{"time":490000,"text":"how come they rule the world?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":494000,"text":"\"Hail to the Gods of America.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":497000,"text":"Hail to the Gods of America!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":499000,"text":"Hail to the gods of the dream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"Invictus E Pluribus Unum."}]},{"cues":[{"time":505000,"text":"But which of them reigns supreme?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"Which is America's Jupiter?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512000,"text":"The Brahmins of Capital Hill?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515000,"text":"A sorcerer's profit on Wall Street?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":519000,"text":"They eye of a dollar bill?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":523000,"text":"Or is it celebrity status?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":525000,"text":"The worship of those we hate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":527000,"text":"Or the cult of living forever,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":529000,"text":"If only we'd watch our weight."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532000,"text":"What of the titans of media?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534000,"text":"Or Hollywood's siren call?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537000,"text":"What of the temples of justice,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":540000,"text":"Whose servants enslave us all?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544000,"text":"What of the Brand and the Label?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":547000,"text":"What of the upstart Sport?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":550000,"text":"And what of the Constitution,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":553000,"text":"That bully of last resort?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":558000,"text":"Hail to the God of America,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":562000,"text":"Whose power the masses extol --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":566000,"text":"Convenience rules America;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":570000,"text":"Convenience owns our soul."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574000,"text":"Aye, that it does."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":581000,"text":"And if you would like to know why I am not a father --"},{"time":583000,"text":"I, who by a miracle have 22 godchildren --"},{"time":590000,"text":"the answer is in this poem,"},{"time":594000,"text":"which upsets me every time I read it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596000,"text":"\"Love Came to Visit Me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":600000,"text":"Love came to visit me,"},{"time":602000,"text":"shy as a fawn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605000,"text":"But finding me busy,"},{"time":607000,"text":"she fled, with the dawn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":611000,"text":"At 20 the torch of resentment was lit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":614000,"text":"My rage at injustice"},{"time":616000,"text":"waxed hot as the pits."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618000,"text":"The flux of its lava cleared all in its path."}]},{"cues":[{"time":621000,"text":"Comrades and enemies fled from its wrath."}]},{"cues":[{"time":626000,"text":"Yet lovers grew wary, once novelty waned"}]},{"cues":[{"time":632000,"text":"To lie with a bloody man,"},{"time":635000,"text":"his terror unfeigned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":639000,"text":"At 30 my powers seemed mighty to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643000,"text":"The fruits of my rivals, I shook from the tree."}]},{"cues":[{"time":646000,"text":"By guile and by bluster,"},{"time":648000,"text":"by night and by day,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":650000,"text":"I battered and scattered the fools from my way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":654000,"text":"And women grew willing to sham and to bluff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":660000,"text":"Their trinkets and baubles cost little enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667000,"text":"From 40 to 50, grown easy and sly,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":670000,"text":"I wined them and dined them, like pigs in a sty."}]},{"cues":[{"time":675000,"text":"We feasted and reveled and rutted in muck,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":677000,"text":"Forgetting our peril, forgetting to duck,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":680000,"text":"Forgetting times arrows are sharper than knives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684000,"text":"Grown sick to our stomachs,"},{"time":688000,"text":"and sick of our lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":691000,"text":"Love came to visit me,"},{"time":694000,"text":"shy as a fawn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":696000,"text":"But finding me busy,"},{"time":699000,"text":"she fled with the dawn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":704000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":714000,"text":"Um, there are --"},{"time":716000,"text":"I've got far too much money and I have far too much fun"},{"time":718000,"text":"in my businesses."},{"time":722000,"text":"So poetry came as a complete shock to me, ladies and gentlemen."},{"time":725000,"text":"A complete shock. I was a little ill."},{"time":728000,"text":"Okay, I was ill."},{"time":730000,"text":"Okay, I had a life-threatening illness, you know."},{"time":733000,"text":"I was in a clinic. I wasn't allowed to make telephone calls."},{"time":738000,"text":"I wasn't allowed to see any of my -- you know, whatever."},{"time":740000,"text":"So, in the end I begged a pack of Post-it notes off a nurse."},{"time":744000,"text":"And from another nurse, I begged a pencil, pen."},{"time":747000,"text":"And I didn't know what else to do. So I started to write poetry."},{"time":750000,"text":"That was in October of 2000."}]},{"cues":[{"time":756000,"text":"I'm not an evil man."},{"time":758000,"text":"But sometimes I try to put myself in an evil man's position."},{"time":761000,"text":"I'm not a glorious and fantastic-looking woman,"},{"time":764000,"text":"who men fall down, you know, when she walks in a room."},{"time":767000,"text":"But sometimes I try to put myself in that position."},{"time":769000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":770000,"text":"Not with much success."},{"time":772000,"text":"But it's interesting to me. I love to write historical verse."},{"time":776000,"text":"I love to think what they thought, what it was like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":779000,"text":"Because although"},{"time":781000,"text":"many of the speakers and many of the people who are in the audience,"},{"time":784000,"text":"although you guys can not only go to the moon,"},{"time":786000,"text":"you know, you're going to totally transform everything."},{"time":788000,"text":"Cloning will transform everything. Voice navigation will transform everything."},{"time":791000,"text":"I don't know. You can do anything you want."},{"time":793000,"text":"All you guys are so clever, and women, you can do it all!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":795000,"text":"But human nature doesn't change, mate."},{"time":799000,"text":"My friends, human nature is exactly the same as it was"},{"time":803000,"text":"when my ancestor --"},{"time":805000,"text":"probably it was my ancestor --"},{"time":808000,"text":"got his hands around the neck of the last Neanderthal,"},{"time":812000,"text":"and battered the bastard to death."},{"time":818000,"text":"You think we didn't do that?"},{"time":820000,"text":"Oh, we did."},{"time":822000,"text":"We killed every single one of them."},{"time":827000,"text":"Inch by inch we killed them."},{"time":829000,"text":"We hunted them down wherever they were."},{"time":833000,"text":"Rivals for meat. Rivals for berries."},{"time":838000,"text":"We're still doing it,"},{"time":840000,"text":"with all of the genius assembled in this room."},{"time":844000,"text":"Our natures haven't changed a single iota."},{"time":848000,"text":"And they never will."},{"time":850000,"text":"Even when we've got off this little planet,"},{"time":856000,"text":"and have put some of our eggs in some other baskets."}]},{"cues":[{"time":863000,"text":"And I am as bad as you."},{"time":866000,"text":"I spent eight years"},{"time":868000,"text":"running one of the most successful publishing businesses in the world."},{"time":872000,"text":"And at seven o'clock every night,"},{"time":874000,"text":"I took me some more girls, already corrupted."},{"time":878000,"text":"I never did anything to anyone that wasn't."},{"time":881000,"text":"And I took crack cocaine,"},{"time":883000,"text":"every single night for seven years."},{"time":888000,"text":"It was like Dante's \"Inferno.\""},{"time":892000,"text":"It was unbelievable."},{"time":896000,"text":"One of the offshoots of crack cocaine is that you keep an erection"},{"time":899000,"text":"for about four hours."},{"time":903000,"text":"And you stay up for 12."},{"time":908000,"text":"It was absolutely unbelievable."},{"time":912000,"text":"Twenty-two godchildren I've got."},{"time":914000,"text":"What do I say to them?"},{"time":917000,"text":"I only stopped because I thought if I got caught,"},{"time":919000,"text":"what would happen to my mother."},{"time":922000,"text":"If you're a woman, remember that."},{"time":925000,"text":"The love of your son"},{"time":928000,"text":"can utterly transform anything he does."}]},{"cues":[{"time":936000,"text":"\"Our Lady in White.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":939000,"text":"Pale she was, listless;"}]},{"cues":[{"time":942000,"text":"And soft to the touch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944000,"text":"A generous mistress Whom many loved much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":947000,"text":"Shoulder to shoulder, Night after night,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":950000,"text":"We hoarded and sold her --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":952000,"text":"Our Lady in White."}]},{"cues":[{"time":954000,"text":"We breathed but to savor"},{"time":957000,"text":"her crystal caress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":959000,"text":"We craved but to favor the hem of her dress."}]},{"cues":[{"time":963000,"text":"We dabbled and babbled,"},{"time":965000,"text":"Denying our thirsts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":968000,"text":"But always we scrabbled"},{"time":971000,"text":"to lie with her first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":974000,"text":"Absent, we missed her,"},{"time":978000,"text":"grew haggard and limp."}]},{"cues":[{"time":980000,"text":"Toyed with her sister,"},{"time":982000,"text":"or threatened her pimp."}]},{"cues":[{"time":984000,"text":"Came word out of Babel, the lady returns!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":987000,"text":"And there on the table we took her, in turns."}]},{"cues":[{"time":992000,"text":"Sensing the power that tyranny craves,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":995000,"text":"There in that hour, she made us her slaves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":998000,"text":"Many there were, to covet her kiss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1005000,"text":"My shame as a spur,"},{"time":1008000,"text":"I fled the abyss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012000,"text":"But only just."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}